(1047, 'Relitch', 254, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Betamethasone (as 17\r\nvalerate) 0.05%,	Phenylephrine\r\nhydrochloride 0.1% &	Lignocaine\r\nhydrochloride 2.5%.</span></p><p><strong>Indication :</strong>Relitch is indicated for:\r\nrelief of the symptoms of itching,\r\nirritation, discomfort or pain associated\r\nwith local non-infective anal or peri-anal\r\nconditions such as external hemorrhoids.Becovent is indicated in the maintenance treatment of asthma as prophylactic therapy in patients 5 years of age and older. Becovent is also indicated for asthma patients who require systemic corticosteroid administration, where adding Becovent may reduce or eliminate the need for the systemic corticosteroids. </p><p><strong>Dosage and administration :</strong>: a course\r\nof treatment should be limited to 7 days.\r\nApply a small amount of ointment two or\r\nthree times a day initially, using the\r\napplicator if internal administration is\r\nrequired. When inflammation is\r\nsubsiding, once-daily application is\r\nsufficient in most cases. Or as directed\r\nby the physicianBecovent inhaler is for oral inhalation use only. Patients should be given a starting dose of inhaled Becovent appropriate to the severity of their disease. The dose may then be adjusted until control is achieved or reduced to the minimum effective dose according to individual response. Management of chronic asthma (Adults & Children over 12 years): 100-400 mcg twice daily. Maximum 1000 mcg twice daily. Children (5-12 years): 100-200 mcg twice daily. the dose may be adjusted as necessary.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Relitch rectal ointment : 15\r\ngram in a tube.</span></p>', 'uploads/images/Relitch.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 04:58:40', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 4, 'uploads/IMG/relitch.jpg'),
(1048, 'Aclene Plus', 256, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong>Each Metered dose (Puff) contains Beclometasone Dipropionate 100 mcg.</p><p><strong>Indication : </strong>Becovent is indicated in the maintenance treatment of asthma as prophylactic therapy in patients 5 years of age and older. Becovent is also indicated for asthma patients who require systemic corticosteroid administration, where adding Becovent may reduce or eliminate the need for the systemic corticosteroids. </p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong>Becovent inhaler is for oral inhalation use only. Patients should be given a starting dose of inhaled Becovent appropriate to the severity of their disease. The dose may then be adjusted until control is achieved or reduced to the minimum effective dose according to individual response. Management of chronic asthma (Adults & Children over 12 years): 100-400 mcg twice daily. Maximum 1000 mcg twice daily. Children (5-12 years): 100-200 mcg twice daily. the dose may be adjusted as necessary.</p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong>Administration of drugs during pregnancy and lactation should only be considered if the expected benefit to the mother is greater than any possible risk to the foetus or child. There is insufficient experience of the use of Salmeterol Xinafoate and Fluticasone Propionate in human pregnancy and lactation. There are no data available for human breast milk.</p><p><strong>Packing : </strong>Becovent HFA Inhaler : Each box contains one inhaler of 200 Puffs</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-09 03:48:11', NULL, NULL, 'Y', 'Y', 4, 'uploads/IMG/aclene.jpg'),
(1049, 'Dalacin-B', 257, '<p><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Clindamycin Phosphate 1.2% and Tretinoin 0.025%. Indications : This gel is indicated for the topical treatment of acne vulgaris in patients 12 years or older.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Clindamycin & tretinoin gel should be applied once daily in the evening, gently rubbing the medication to lightly cover the entire affected area. Approximately a pea sized amount will be needed for each application. Avoid the eyes, lips, and mucous membranes. Clindamycin & tretinoin gel is not for oral, ophthalmic or intravaginal use. Or, as directered by registered physician.</span></p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">There are no controlled data in women pregnancy. It can be used in pregnancy if potential benefits outweigh the risk or as directed by the registered physician. Clindamycin is likely to be excreted into the breast milk. A decision should be made whether to discontinue nursing or to discontinue the drug, taking into account the benefit of the drug to the mother. Pregnancy Category B.</span></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space" style="background-color: initial;">Dalacin Plus Gel : 15gm in a tube.</span></p>', 'uploads/images/DalacinPlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 03:57:53', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 4, 'uploads/IMG/dalacin-plus-gel.jpg'),
(1050, 'Dalacin Plus', 258, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Clindamycin Phosphate\r\n1.2% and Tretinoin 0.025%.\r\nIndications : This gel is indicated for the\r\ntopical treatment of acne vulgaris in\r\npatients 12 years or older.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Clindamycin & tretinoin gel should be\r\napplied once daily in the evening, gently\r\nrubbing the medication to lightly cover\r\nthe entire affected area. Approximately a\r\npea sized amount will be needed for\r\neach application. Avoid the eyes, lips,\r\nand mucous membranes. Clindamycin &\r\ntretinoin gel is not for oral, ophthalmic or\r\nintravaginal use. Or, as directered by\r\nregistered physician.</span></p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">There are no controlled data in women\r\npregnancy. It can be used in pregnancy if\r\npotential benefits outweigh the risk or as\r\ndirected by the registered physician.\r\nClindamycin is likely to be excreted into\r\nthe breast milk. A decision should be\r\nmade whether to discontinue nursing or\r\nto discontinue the drug, taking into\r\naccount the benefit of the drug to the\r\nmother. Pregnancy Category B.</span></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Dalacin Plus Gel : 15gm in a\r\ntube.</span></p>', 'uploads/images/DalacinPlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 03:57:20', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 4, 'uploads/IMG/dalacin-plus-gel.jpg'),
(1051, 'Diproxen', 259, '<p><strong>Composition : </strong>: Naproxen Sodium 10%.</p><p><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">This gel is indicated for treatment of rheumatoid arthritis, osteoarthritis, ankylosing spondylitis, tendonitis, bursitis, acute gout, and the management of mild to moderate pain and primary dysmenorrhoea.</span></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Diproxen Gel is to be applied 2-6 times a day as required and is not recommended for use in children. Or, as directed by the registered physician</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Packing :</strong>Diproxen Gel : 15gm in a tube.</p>', 'uploads/images/Dovonex.jpg', 1, '2017-12-03 00:10:09', NULL, NULL, 'Y', 'Y', 4, 'uploads/IMG/diproxen.jpg'),
(1052, 'Micoderm', 260, '<p><strong>Composition : </strong>Miconazole 2%</p><p><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">This gel is indicated for oral treatment and prevention of fungal infections of the oropharynx and of super infections due to Grampositive bacteria.</span></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">For localized lesions of the mouth, a small amount of gel may be applied directly to the affected area with a clean finger. For topical treatment of the oropharynx, the gel should be kept in the mouth for as long as possible. Treatment should be continued for up to 2 days after the symptoms have cleared. For oral candidosis, dental prostheses should be removed at night and brushed with the gel. Or, as directed by the registered physician.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space" style="background-color: initial;">Micoderm Oral Gel : 15gm in a tube</span></p>', 'uploads/images/Micoderm.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 03:33:48', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 4, 'uploads/IMG/micoderm-gel.jpg'),
(1053, 'Trialon Oral Paste', 147, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Triamcinolone Acetonide\r\n0.1%.</span></p><p><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">It is indicated for aphthous\r\nulcers, ulcerative stomatitis, denture\r\nstomatitis, desquamative gingivitis,\r\nerosive lichen planus and lesions of the\r\noral mucosa of traumatic origin.</span></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Adults and\r\nChildren : To be applied to the lesion at\r\nbedtime and two to four times daily,\r\npreferably after meals. Apply to the\r\naffected area; do not rub in.\r\nElderly : Corticosteroids should be used\r\nsparingly and for short periods of time. or\r\nas directed by the registered physician</span></p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Triamcinolone should only be prescribed\r\nwhen the benefits to the mother & child\r\noutweigh the risks. Some of\r\ncorticosteroids may pass into breast\r\nmilk, but no data are available for\r\nTriamcinolone Acetonide. Pregnancy\r\nCategory C.</span></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Trialon Oral Paste : 10 gram\r\nin a tube.</span></p>', 'uploads/images/TrialonOralPaste.jpg', 1, '2017-11-27 04:56:07', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 4, 'uploads/IMG/trilone.jpg'),
(1054, 'Alocap ', 302, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each Soft Capsule Contains Aloe Vera Extract 100mg (200:1 Concentrate)</span></p><p><strong>Indication : </strong></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Take one capsule one to three times daily, preferably with a meal. Or, as directed by the\r\nregistered physician.</span></p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong>Aloe vera is not recommended for pregnant and lactating women.</p><p><strong>Packing : </strong>Each Box Contains 5 x 10''s soft capsules in blister pack.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-26 06:50:59', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/Alocap.jpg'),
(1055, 'Anros', 303, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong>Each capsule contains andrographis (Andrographis paniculata) 200 mg</p><p><strong>Indication :</strong></p><p><strong></strong>Andrographis is indicated in the treatment of following diseases-\r\n* Flu\r\n* Antiviral (Influenza,Hepatitis B,Herpes)\r\n* Common cold\r\n* Sinusitis\r\n* Upper respiratory tract infection (Sore throat, pharyngotonsillitis, bronchitis)\r\n* Stimulates the immune system\r\n* Antihepatotoxic\r\n* Hepato-biliary protective\r\n* Antipyretic\r\n* Antityphoid\r\n* Antifungal\r\n* Antihelminthic</p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong>1-2 Capsules 2-3 times daily after meals or as directed by the registered physician</p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong>Do not take during pregnancy.</p><p><strong>Packing : </strong>Each box contains 10 x 4 = 40 capsules in Alu-Alu blister pack.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-30 04:28:31', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/ANROS-Capsule.jpg'),
(1056, 'Biloba', 304, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong>Each capsule contains 60 mg standardized extract of Ginkgo biloba.</p><p><strong>Indication : </strong></p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Primary uses\r\nCerebral Insufficiency : Memory deficit, depression, attention and memory loss that occur\r\nwith Alzheimer''s disease and multi-infarct dementia.</span></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong>1 or 2 Capsule 2 to 3 times daily or as advised by the registered physician.</p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong>There is no known restriction of the use of ginkgo in pregnancy and lactation</p><p><strong>Packing : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Biloba 60mg capsule\r\nEach box contains 32 capsules in 8 X 4 Alu-Alu blister packs.</span></p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 05:17:09', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/biloba.jpg');
INSERT INTO `drg_medicine_info` (`MEDICINE_ID`, `MEDICINE_NAME`, `GN_GRP_ID`, `MEDICINE_DESC`, `INSERT_FILE`, `CRE_BY`, `CRE_DT`, `UPD_BY`, `UPD_DT`, `IS_LATEST`, `ACTIVE_STATUS`, `CAT_ID`, `PRODUCT_FET_PHOTO`) VALUES
(1057, 'Biogut', 305, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition :</strong></p><p><strong></strong>Biogut 250 : Each Capsule Contains Saccharomyces boulardii 250 mg (Eq.to 5 billion CFU). </p><p>Biogut 500 : Each Capsule Contains Saccharomyces boulardii 500 mg (Eq.to 10 billion CFU).</p><p><strong>Indication :</strong></p><p><strong> </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">It is indicatedl\r\nPrevention of diarrhoea associated with antibiotics </span></p><p>Reduction in symptoms of acute diarrhea</p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Prevention of traveler''s diarrhea </span></p><p>Treating diarrhea in infants</p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Prevention of HIV associated diarrhea </span></p><p>Preventing recurring intestinal disease caused by a bacterium called Clostridium difficile </p><p>Reducing side effects of treatment for the ulcer - causing bacterium Helicobacter pylori</p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Treating diarrhea in Crohn''s disease </span></p><p>Treating diarrhea in Ulcerative colitis </p><p>Treating diarrhea in Irritable bowel syndrome (IBS)</p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong></p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Adult : For diarrhea associated with the use of antibiotics : 250-500 mg of Saccharomyces boulardii two to\r\nfour times a day.\r\nFor diarrhea caused by Clostridium difficile : 1 gram of Saccharomyces boulardii daily for 4 weeks along\r\nwith antibiotic treatment.\r\nFor reduction in symptoms of acute diarrhea : 250 mg of Saccharomyces boulardii twice a day for 5 days.</span></p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">There is no available information about the safety of taking Saccharomyces boulardii in pregnancy and\r\nlactation. If needed during pregnancy and lactation consult the registered physician.</span></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong></p><p><strong></strong>Biogut 250 : Each box contains 5x4=20 capsules in Alu-Alu blister pack. </p><p>Biogut 500 : Each box contains 5x4=20 capsules in Alu-Alu blister pack.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-30 04:38:16', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/Biogut-250.jpg'),
(1058, 'Dalion', 306, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong>Each capsule contains Dandelion 425mg.</p><p><strong>Indication :</strong></p><p><strong></strong>Dandelion is indicated for- </p><p>* Dyspeptic complaints </p><p>* Infection of the urinary tract</p><p>\r\n* Liver & gallbladder complaints </p><p>* Loss of appetiteBecovent is indicated in the maintenance treatment of asthma as prophylactic therapy in patients 5 years of age and older. Becovent is also indicated for asthma patients who require systemic corticosteroid administration, where adding Becovent may reduce or eliminate the need for the systemic corticosteroids. </p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong>1-2 Capsules 2-3 times daily,Or, as directed by the registered physician</p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong>No experience is available about the use of Dandelion in pregnant & lactating mother.</p><p><strong>Packing :</strong>Each box contains 8 x 4 = 32 capsules in Alu-Alu blister pack.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 03:49:38', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/dalion.jpg'),
(1059, 'Devas', 307, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each teaspoon full (5 ml) of DEVAS syrup contains extracts of -\r\nAdhatoda vasica 0.68 gm, Piper longum 0.14 gm, Glycyrrhiza glabra 6.78 mg,\r\nTrikatu (Piper nigrum, Zingiber officinale) 20.34 mg, Terminalia chebula 73.24 mg,\r\nVitis venifera 0.14 gm, Acorus calamus 6.78 mg, Saussurea lappa 6.78 mg,\r\nSyzygium aromaticum 6.78 mg, Trizatak (Cinnamomum zeylanicum, Elettaria\r\ncardamomum, Cinnamomum tamala) 20.34 mg, Pistacia integerrima 6.78 mg,\r\nMyrica nagi 6.78 mg,Woodfordia fruticosa 1.14 mg</span></p><p><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">DEVAS syrup liquefies phlegm. It sooths irritation of throat. Helps to relieve hoarseness. It is a remedy for all types of\r\ncough such as dry irritable cough, allergic & smokers cough.</span></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Children under 12 years :1-2 teaspoonful ( 5-10 ml ) 2-3 times a day.Adult :3 teaspoonful ( 15 ml ) 2-3 times a day.\r\nSome warm water may be added for better result.</span></p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong>The safety of DEVAS syrup in pregnancy has not been studied. Therefore, it should be used with caution during\r\npregnancy.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 03:47:18', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/devas.jpg'),
(1060, 'Devas', 307, '<p><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each teaspoon full (5 ml) of DEVAS syrup contains extracts of - Adhatoda vasica 0.68 gm, Piper longum 0.14 gm, Glycyrrhiza glabra 6.78 mg, Trikatu (Piper nigrum, Zingiber officinale) 20.34 mg, Terminalia chebula 73.24 mg, Vitis venifera 0.14 gm, Acorus calamus 6.78 mg, Saussurea lappa 6.78 mg, Syzygium aromaticum 6.78 mg, Trizatak (Cinnamomum zeylanicum, Elettaria cardamomum, Cinnamomum tamala) 20.34 mg, Pistacia integerrima 6.78 mg, Myrica nagi 6.78 mg,Woodfordia fruticosa 1.14 mg</span></p><p><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">DEVAS syrup liquefies phlegm. It sooths irritation of throat. Helps to relieve hoarseness. It is a remedy for all types of cough such as dry irritable cough, allergic & smokers cough.</span></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Children under 12 years :1-2 teaspoonful ( 5-10 ml ) 2-3 times a day.Adult :3 teaspoonful ( 15 ml ) 2-3 times a day. Some warm water may be added for better result.</span></p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong>The safety of DEVAS syrup in pregnancy has not been studied. Therefore, it should be used with caution during pregnancy.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 03:47:40', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/devas.jpg'),
(1061, 'Dort', 308, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong>Each capsule contains 300 mg standardized extract of St.John''s wort.</p><p><strong>Indication : </strong> </p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space">DORT capsule is indicated to Mental depression, Anxiety, Sleeping disturbance (Insomnia),\r\nFatigue, Seasonal affected disorder (SAD). It enhances Memory, Mental concentration &\r\nReceptivity.</span></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong>1 capsule 3 times daily or as advised by the registered physician.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 03:45:53', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/dort.jpg'),
(1062, 'Garlicap', 309, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong>Each soft gelatin enteric coated capsule contains Garlic Oil 10 mg.</p><p><strong>Indication : </strong> </p><p>1. Hyperlipidemia </p><p>2. Arteriosclerosis</p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space">\r\n3. Hypertension</span></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Hyperlipidemia and arteriosclerosis : 2-3 capsules daily.\r\nHypertension : 1 capsule three times daily.</span></p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong>No teratogenic effect is found. Not recommended during lactation.</p><p><br></p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 02:42:06', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/garlicap.jpg'),
(1063, 'Ginax', 310, '<p><strong></strong><strong>The pregnant mothers should consult their physician before using Ginax capsule.Composition : </strong>Each capsule contains Panax ginseng 500 mg standardized extract.</p><p><strong>Indication : </strong> </p><p>Ginax is indicated</p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space">l\r\nTo reduce fatigue and stress</span></p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space">\r\nl Increase vitality strengthens immunity aphordicise </span></p><p>l Erectile dysfunction and fertility </p><p>l Menopausal symptoms </p><p>l Non-insulin dependent diabetes mellitus </p><p>l Helps to prevents senile dementia.</p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong></p><p>1 Ginax capsule 1 - 2 times a day or as advised by the physician.</p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong></p><p>The pregnant mothers should consult their physician before using Ginax capsule.</p><p><br></p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 02:43:50', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/GINAX-Capsule.jpg'),
(1064, 'Hepanor', 311, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong></p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space"><strong>Hepanor 70 :</strong> Each capsule contains Silymarin 70 mg,\r\nwhich is the dried extract of milk thistle fruits<strong>.</strong></span></p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space"><strong>\r\nHepanor 140 : </strong>Each capsule contains Silymarin USP 140mg,\r\nwhich is the powdered milk thistle extract<strong>.</strong></span></p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space"><strong>\r\nHepanor 500 : </strong>Each capsule contains Silymarin 500 mg,which is\r\nthe dried extract of milk thistle fruits.</span></p><p><strong>Indication : </strong></p><p>* Toxic liver damage for supportive treatment in patients with jaundice </p><p>* Chronic inflammatory liver conditions, i.e.hepatities </p><p>* Alcoholic liver damage and hepatic cirrhosis.</p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong></p><p><strong>Hepanor 70 :</strong> 1 - 2 capsules 2 to 3 times daily<strong>.</strong></p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space"><strong>\r\nHepanor 140 : </strong>1 capsule should be taken 2 - 3 times daily.<strong> </strong></span></p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space"><strong>Hepanor 500 : </strong>1 capsule daily.\r\nThe medication should be continued until the relief of the symptoms according to the advice\r\nof a physician.Or, as directed by the registered physician.</span></p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">No experience is available with regard to the use of silymarin during pregnancy and lactation.\r\nTherefore, it should only be used after an accurate diagnosis has been made by the treating\r\ndoctor</span></p><p><strong>Packing :</strong><em></em></p><p><em>Hepanor-70 : </em>Each box contains 8 X 4 = 32 capsules in Alu-Alu blister pack.<em>\r\nHepanor-140 :</em> Each box contains 5 X 4 = 20 capsules in Alu-Alu blister pack.<em><strong>\r\n</strong>Hepanor-500 :</em> Each box contains 5 X 4 = 20 capsules in Alu-Alu blister pack.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-27 23:42:57', NULL, NULL, 'Y', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/hepnaor.jpg'),
(1065, 'Melbit', 313, '<p><strong>Composition : </strong>Each capsule contains Bitter Melon (korola) 400mg.</p><p><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Regulate Blood sugar level, Improve pancreatic & liver function, boost immunity & natural\r\nsource of vitamin C.Helps in easy digestion.</span></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration :</strong>1-2 Capsules twice daily 20-30 minutes after meals or as advised by the registered physician.Becovent inhaler is for oral inhalation use only. Patients should be given a starting dose of inhaled Becovent appropriate to the severity of their disease. The dose may then be adjusted until control is achieved or reduced to the minimum effective dose according to individual response. Management of chronic asthma (Adults & Children over 12 years): 100-400 mcg twice daily. Maximum 1000 mcg twice daily. Children (5-12 years): 100-200 mcg twice daily. the dose may be adjusted as necessary.</p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong>Bitter melon should not be used in pregnant & lactating mother.</p><p><strong>Packing :</strong>Each box contains 10 x 4 = 40 Capsules in Alu-Alu blister pack</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 03:41:44', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/AclenePlus.jpg'),
(1066, 'Laxadil', 312, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Laxadil Sachet : Each sachet contains\r\nIspaghula husk 3.50 gm.</span></p><p><strong>Indication :</strong></p><p><strong></strong>l Constipation</p><p>\r\nl Irritable bowels syndrome (IBS )</p><p>\r\nl Rectal bleeding (Piles)</p><p>\r\nl Helps healing ulcer of mucous membrane of stomach</p><p>\r\nl Helps reducing blood cholesterol </p><p><strong>Dosage and administration :</strong><em> Adult : </em>One sachet 1-3 times daily, children : Half dose of an adult or as directed by the\r\nregistered physician.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 02:25:38', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/laxadil.jpg'),
(1067, 'Mintek', 314, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong>Each Soft Gelatin Enteric Coated Capsule Contains Peppermint Oil 0.2ml.</p><p><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Peppermint oil relaxes gastrointestinal smooth muscle and relieves flatulence and colic. It is\r\nalso used in irritable bowel syndrome (IBS).</span></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Adult : One capsule three times daily for up to 2-3 months, increased to two capsules three\r\ntimes daily if necessary. The capsule should be taken half to one hour before taking food or as\r\ndirected by a registered physician.</span></p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong></p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space">There are no adequate and well-controlled studies in pregnant women. It is not known\r\nwhether peppermint oil is excreted in human milk.</span></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong>Each box contains 5 x 10 = 50 soft capsules in blister pack.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 03:43:48', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/mintek.jpg'),
(1068, 'Nacea', 315, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong>Each capsule contains Echinacea purpurea 400 mg</p><p><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Echinacea is used for cold and chronic infection of the respiratory tract & urinary tract. It may\r\nalso use influenza like infection, Immune modulation and wound healing effects.</span></p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong>1 Capsules twice daily after meals or as directed by the registered physician</p><p><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong></p><p>Do not take during pregnancy</p><p><strong>Packing : </strong>Each box contains 8 x 4 = 32 capsules in Alu-Alu blister pack</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 04:18:29', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/nacea.jpg'),
(1069, 'Palmetto', 316, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong>Each capsule contains Saw palmetto (Serenoa repens) fruit 500 mg</p><p><strong>Indication : </strong>Urination problems in benign prostatic hyperplasia stages I & II</p><p><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong>1 to 2 gm (2-4 capsules) in divided doses daily or as advised by the registered physician.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong>Each box contains 8 x 4 = 32 capsules in Alu-Alu blister pack.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 04:35:04', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/palmetto.jpg'),
(1071, 'Primacap-1000', 317, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Primacap : Each soft gelatin capsule contains Evening Primrose Oil 500 mg.\r\nPrimacap-1000 : Each soft gelatin capsule contains Evening Primrose Oil 1000 mg</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong></strong>* Premenstrual syndrome symptoms (PMS) </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Benign breast disease & cyckical mastalgia </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Lactation</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><span class="redactor-invisible-space">\r\n* Atopic, allergic & neurodermatitis</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><span class="redactor-invisible-space">\r\n* Psoriasis </span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Hypertension</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><span class="redactor-invisible-space">\r\n* Rheumatoid arthritis </span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Thrombosis </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Atopic eczema </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Dietary aid </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Promotes healthy skin, nourishes brittle nail & hair.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration :</strong> </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Primacap : One or two capsules two to three times daily or as directed by the registered physician. </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Primacap-1000 : Atopic & Allergic Dermatitis : Adult Dosage : 1 Capsule 2 Times daily. </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Children Dosage : 1 Capsule 1/2 times daily.\r\nBenign</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""> Breast Disease & Mastagia : 1 Capsule 2/3 times daily with or after meal. </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Premenstrual Syndrome (PMS) : 1 Capsule 2 times daily at morning & night with or after meal. </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Rheumatoid arthritis : 1 Capsule daily. Or as directed by the registered physician.</p><p><br></p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 04:32:45', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/primacap.jpg'),
(1072, 'Spirucap', 319, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong>Each capsule contains Spirulina dry powder 500 mg</p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong></strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">1) Spirucap promotes formation and development of blood cells and thus effective in\r\nanemia. </span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">2) It is hepatoprotective and hypocholesterolemic. </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">3) Spirucap helps to maintain healthy skin and slows aging process.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><span class="redactor-invisible-space">\r\n4) Spirucap is antiviral. It improves immunity.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong>4 - 6 capsules per day or as advised by the registered physician</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><br></p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 05:13:02', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/spirucap.jpg'),
(1073, 'Thyvy', 320, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each 5ml syrup contains Ivy leaf dry extract 37.5mg and\r\nThyme dry extract 50mg.</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication :</strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong></strong>Relieves Cough (chesty & mucosal) </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Liquefies Mucus\r\nHelps in Bronchitis (Catarrh or inflammation of the respiratory tract) </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Relieves shortness of breath</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration :</strong> </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Children (6-9 years) & adolescents (&gt;10 years) : Take 5ml (1 tea spoonful) 3 times daily. </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Adults : Take 5-7.5ml (1-11/2 tea spoonful) 3 times daily.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><span class="redactor-invisible-space">\r\nDuration of treatment : Duration of treatment depends on the type and severity of the\r\nclinical picture; however treatment should continue for at least one week even in minor\r\ninflammations of the respiratory tract. Treatment with this syrup should be maintained for 2-3\r\ndays after symptoms have subsided, in order to insure lasting success of therapy. Or, as\r\ndirected by the registered physician.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation :</strong> <strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><span class="redactor-invisible-space">This medicine should be taken during pregnancy and breast-feeding only after having\r\npreviously consulted doctor.</span></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong>100 ml in PET bottle.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-12-04 04:01:26', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 6, 'uploads/IMG/AclenePlus.jpg'),
(1074, 'Amlabery', 289, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong></p><p><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each 5ml syrup contains extracts of Phyllanthus emblica 500.00 mg,\r\nPiper nigrum 20.00 mg, Pistacia integerrima 20.00 mg, Chlorophytum arundinaceum 20.00 mg,\r\nMesua Ferrea 20.00 mg, Glycyrrhiza glabra 10.00 mg, Withania somnifera 20.00 mg, Cyperus\r\nrotundus 5.00 mg, Elettaria cardamomum 10.00 mg, Syzygium aromaticum 5.00 mg,\r\nCinnamomum zeylanicum 5.00 mg, Ocimum album 5.00 mg, Potassium Carbonatum 5.00 mg,\r\nAdhatoda vasica 10.00 mg, Lycium barbarum 10.00 mg, Vitex nigundu 10.00 mg, Piper cubeba\r\n10.00 mg, Piper Longum 100.00 mg, Aegle marmelos 10.00 mg, Tribulus terrestris 20.00 mg,\r\nZingiber officinale 50.00 mg & other ingredients q.s.\r\nUses :\r\nVitamin C deficiency diseases, cough, cold, general weakness, nervous debility, mental fatigue,\r\nweakness of memory, indigestion, malnutrition and leanness</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Adult : 2-4 teaspoonfuls 1-2 times daily after meal.\r\nChildren : 1-2 teaspoonfuls 1-2 times daily after meal. Or, as directed by the registered\r\nphysician.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">The safety of syrup Amlabery in pregnancy has not been studied. Therefore, it should be used\r\nwith caution during pregnancy.</span><strong></strong></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong>450 ml in PET bottle.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 05:37:35', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 5, 'uploads/IMG/amlaberry.jpg'),
(1075, 'Centrica', 290, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each capsule contains Centella asiatica 250 mg.\r\n</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">It is effective in skin diseases, leprosy wound and dysentery. It helps to improve memory and\r\nfunction of brain & regulate blood pressure.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong>1-2 capsules twice daily or as directed by the registered physician.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">The safety of penitab in pregnancy has not been established.Therefore, it should be used with\r\ncaution during pregnancy.</span><strong></strong></p><p><br></p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 04:34:19', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 5, 'uploads/IMG/Centrica-Capsule.jpg'),
(1076, 'D-Alovera ', 291, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each 5ml syrup contains 600mg fresh inner leaf gel of Ghritokumari\r\n(Aloevera).</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Aloevera is used for the treatment of liver inflammation,weakness of\r\nliver function, general weakness, gastrointestinal disorders, improves\r\nimmune system, constipation, digestion problem,fungal diseases,\r\nskin freshness,skin diseases,weight loss, amenorrhea,worm infestation and infections</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Adult: 3 to 5 teaspoonfuls syrup 2 times daily, preferably with a meal.Or as directed by the\r\nregistered physician.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong>Aloevera is not recommended for pregnant and lactating women.<strong></strong></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong>100 ml & 450 ml in PET bottle.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 03:44:42', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 5, 'uploads/IMG/D-alovera.jpg'),
(1077, 'Difans', 292, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each 5ml syrup contains extract of\r\nPiper nigrum 150mg, Trachyspermum ammi 100mg, Citrus aurantifolia 100mg, Cinnamomum\r\nzeylanicum 50mg, Emblica officinalis 50mg, Terminalia belerica 38mg, Terminalia chebula\r\n38mg, Zingiber officinale 10mg, Sea salt 8mg and other ingrediets QS. Ref: B.N.U.F.</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Digestive and carminative to correct indigestion, dyspepsia, flatulence, constipation,\r\nabdominal pain due to gases,stomach and liver disorders.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration :</strong><em> </em></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><em>Adults : </em>2 teaspoonfuls 2-3 times daily<em>.</em></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><em>\r\nChildren : </em>1/2 - 1 teaspoonful 2-3 times daily or as directed by the registered physician.<br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation :</strong> The safety of Hazmina in pregnancy has not been established. Therefore, it should be used\r\nwith caution during pregnancy.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 03:43:19', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 5, 'uploads/IMG/difans.jpg'),
(1078, 'D-sefa', 293, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong>Each soft gelatin capsule contains Black Seed Oil 500mg.</p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">D-Sefa is indicated for the treatment of common cold, cough, asthma, bronchitis,\r\nmuscle spasm,fever, dyspepsia, vomiting, gout, insufficient breast milk, eczema and wound. It is\r\nalso used to improve immune system, reduce blood sugar, blood pressure & stop hair loss.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">1 capsule 2-3 times daily.\r\nOr, as directed by the registered physician.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Black seed oil is not recommended during pregnancy. In lactating mother it should be taken to\r\nincrease breast milk of mother.</span><strong></strong></p><p><br></p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 03:41:42', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 5, 'uploads/IMG/d-sefa.jpg'),
(1079, 'Hemosaf', 294, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each 5 ml Syrup contains extract ofCassia\r\nangustifolia 17.00 mg, Rheum emodi 13.00\r\nmg, Cassia sophera 12.50 mg, Ocimum sanctum 2.50\r\nmg, Operculina turpethum 2.00 mg, Rosa damascena\r\n2.00 mg, Sphaeranthus indicus 2.00 mg, Gentiana\r\nkurroo 2.00 mg, Fumaria parviflora 2.00 mg, Clitoria\r\nternatea 2.00 mg, Artemisia absinthium 2.00 mg,\r\nNymphaea alba 1.25 mg, Dalbergia sissoo 1.25 mg,\r\nPterocarpus santalinus 1.25 mg, Tinospora cordifolia\r\n1.25 mg, Terminalia chebula 1.25 mg, Zingiber zerumbet 1.25mg, Swertia chirata 1.25\r\nmg, Andographis paniculata 1.25 mg, Bauhinia racemosa 1.25 mg, Azadirachta indica\r\n1.25 mg, Curcuma longa 1.25 mg and other ingredients QS.</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Acne vulgaris, pimples and boils, skin eruptions, impurities in blood, chronic\r\n& temporary constipation, general lassitude, heat rash and itching, epistaxis, measles,\r\nburning sensation during urination and also as an immunostimulant.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong>: 2-4 teaspoonfuls 1-2 times daily.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><br></p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 02:46:20', NULL, NULL, 'Y', 'Y', 5, 'uploads/IMG/hemosaf.jpg'),
(1080, 'Jarira', 295, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong>Each Capsule Contains Chirata (Swertia chirata) 250mg.</p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Dyspepsia,Appetite Suppressant, gastric juice secretion & gastrointestinal tract disturbance. </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Control acidity, gas, indigestion, naturally.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">\r\n* Controls blood sugar.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">\r\n* Reduce intermittent & remittent fever.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">\r\n* Reduce obesity & cholesterol naturally. </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Anti-allergic agent & protects liver & kidney naturally. </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* lt is useful in skin diseases like acne, pimples and other infections of skin.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">\r\n* Develops immunity. </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Long term uses of Jarira capsule destroy intestinal worms.<br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration :</strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">1-2 Capsules 2-3 times daily.\r\nOr, as directed by the registered physician.</span> </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation :</strong> Administration of drugs during pregnancy and lactation should only be considered if the expected benefit to the mother is greater than any possible risk to the foetus or child. There is insufficient experience of the use of Salmeterol Xinafoate and Fluticasone Propionate in human pregnancy and lactation. There are no data available for human breast milk.<strong></strong></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong>Becovent HFA Inhaler : Each box contains one inhaler of 200 Puffs</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 02:48:44', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 5, 'uploads/IMG/jarira.jpg'),
(1081, 'Livro', 296, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each 5ml syrup contains extract of Cichorium endivia\r\n(Root) 400mg, Cichorium endivia (Seed) 200mg, Rosa\r\ndamascena 200mg, Nymphaea alba 100mg, Borago officinalis 100mg, Cuscuta reflexa 150mg,\r\nRheum emodi 125mg.</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong>Hepatitis,Obstructive Jaundice,Ascitis,Constipation, Pleurisy & Metritis</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Adults: 2-3 teaspoonfuls twice daily.\r\nChildren : 1/2-1 teaspoonful twice daily after meal or as directed by the registered physician.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">No experience is available with regard to the use during pregnancy and lactation. Therefore, it\r\nshould only be used after an accurate diagnosis has been made by the treating doctor.</span><strong></strong></p><p><br></p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 02:51:41', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 5, 'uploads/IMG/Livro-Syrup.jpg'),
