(1083, 'Ridex', 298, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each capsule containsMyristica\r\nfragrans (arillus)	66.66 mg\r\nLacerta agilis	66.66 mg\r\nArgyreia speciosa	33.33 mg\r\nMyristica fragrans (nut)	33.33 mg\r\nCalcined silver	16.66 mg\r\nCrocus sativus	16.66 mg\r\nMineral bezoar	8.33 mg\r\nCastoreum	8.33 mg\r\nand other ingredients\r\nRef: Habbe Nishat\r\nBangladesh National Unani Formulary</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Sexual weakness, Premature ejaculation, Nervous debility, General\r\nweakness.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Usually one capsule in the morning and one capsule at\r\nbed time or two capsules to be taken with milk or honey 2 hours before coitus daily or as\r\ndirected by the registered physician. Ridex should be continued at least 3-4 weeks for\r\noptimum result. For better result patients are advised following mode of administration:\r\n2+0+2 Capsules for 5 days then 2+0+1 capsules for 10 days followed by 1+0+1 capsule\r\nas maintenance dose. Continuous use of Ridex may serve as a good general restorative\r\ntonic. For complete functional impotence it is necessary to increase the above dosage of\r\nRidex to 2 capsules t.i.d. This should be done under constant supervision. or, as directed\r\nby the registered physician.</span></p><br><p><strong>Packing :</strong><em> </em><span class="redactor-invisible-space"><em>Ridex : </em>Each box contains 5 x 4 = 20 capsules in Alu-Alu blister pack.\r\n</span></p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 04:56:37', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 5, 'uploads/IMG/ridex.jpg');
