(1084, 'Tifal', 299, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each 5ml syrup containsPimpinella\r\nanisum (Anise)\r\nAnethum sowa (Sowa Seed) 0.002 ml\r\nAmomum subulatum (Greater cardamom)\r\nMentha arvensis (Mint)\r\nAnise oil (Anise oil) 0.0035 ml\r\nHordeum vulgare (Barley) 40.00 mg\r\nand other ingredients QS\r\nReference : BNUF</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Flatulence, diarrhea and indigestion,stomach disorder & discomfort of infants & children\r\nduring teething.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Up to 6 months :</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><span class="redactor-invisible-space"> 1/2 teaspoonfull syrup 3 - 4 times daily.6 months to 1 year :\r\n1 teaspoonfull syrup 3 - 4 times daily.1 to 2 year : 1 - 2 teaspoonfull syrup 3 - 4 times daily.Or\r\nas directed by the registered physician.</span></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong>100 ml in PET bottle.</p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-12-04 03:59:32', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 5, 'uploads/IMG/tifal.jpg'),
(1085, 'Tims', 300, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each 5ml syrup contains extract ofSaraca\r\nindica (Ashok) 250.00mg\r\nWithania somnifera (Winter cherry) 125.00mg\r\nSmilax china (China root) 62.50mg\r\nAbroma augusta (Devil''s cotton) 62.50mg\r\nRauwolfia serpentina (Snake root) 50.00mg\r\nFerrum (Iron) 10.00mg</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Menstrual irregularities</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Dysmenorrhoea </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Amenorrhoea </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Leucorrhoea</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Metritis</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">Uterine inflammation & anaemia</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">2 tea-spoonfuls at bedtime with lukewarm water. In chronic cases additional 2 tea-spoonfuls in\r\nthe morning as well. If necessary 4 tea spoonfuls twice daily can be given with the\r\nrecommendation of the registered physician.Not recommended for children. or, as directed by\r\nthe registered physician.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><br></p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-12-04 03:58:08', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 5, 'uploads/IMG/tims.jpg'),
(1086, 'Zurid', 301, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each 5ml syrup contains extract ofCichorium\r\nintybus (Root) 250.00 mg\r\nCucumis melo (Seed) 250.00 mg\r\nFoeniculum vulgare (Root) 125.00 mg\r\nFoeniculum vulgare (Seed) 125.00 mg\r\nCichorium intybus (Seed) 125.00 mg\r\nTribulusterrestris 125.00 mg</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication :</strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong></strong>* Pyrexia\r\n* Oliguria </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Amenorrhoea </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Hepatitis </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* Obstructive jaundice </p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"="">* It is very effective to clear the morbid substances from the kidney and urinary bladder.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration :</strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Adult : 2-4 teaspoonfuls two to four times daily.\r\nChildren : 1-2 teaspoonfuls two to four times daily.\r\nOr, as directed by the registered physician.\r\n</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><br></p>', 'uploads/images/AclenePlus.jpg', 1, '2017-11-28 02:02:11', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 5, 'uploads/IMG/zurid.jpg'),
(1087, 'Ferozi-CI', 323, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Each Time Release\r\nCapsule Contains Elemental Iron 50mg\r\n(as Carbony Iron), Folic Acid 0.50mg and\r\nZinc Sulphate Monohydrate 61.80mg.</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication :</strong>It is indicated for the\r\ntreatment and prophylaxis of Iron, Folic\r\nAcid and Zinc deficiency specially during\r\npregnancy and lactation.Becovent is indicated in the maintenance treatment of asthma as prophylactic therapy in patients 5 years of age and older. Becovent is also indicated for asthma patients who require systemic corticosteroid administration, where adding Becovent may reduce or eliminate the need for the systemic corticosteroids.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Adults:\r\nOne capsule daily before food. Or as\r\ndirected by the registered physician.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Use\r\nof any drug during the first trimester of\r\npregnancy should be avoided if possible.\r\nThus administration of iron during the\r\nfirst trimester requires definite evidence\r\nof iron deficiency. Prophylaxis of iron\r\ndeficiency where inadequate diet calls\r\nfor supplementary zinc and folic acid is\r\njustified during the remainder of\r\npregnancy.</span><strong></strong></p><p><strong>Packing :<em> </em></strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space"><em>Ferozi-CI TR Capsule :\r\n</em>5x10''s capsules in blister pack.</span></p>', 'uploads/images/ferozi_ci.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 02:55:11', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 4, 'uploads/IMG/ferozi-ci.jpg'),
(1088, 'Ferospan', 321, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Ferospan timed release\r\ncapsule is a combination of blended\r\npellets of dried Ferrous Sulphate 150mg\r\nand Folic Acid 500mcg.</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Ferospan is indicated for\r\nthe treatment and prophylaxis of iron and\r\nfolic acid deficiency, specially during\r\npregnancy and lactation.\r\n</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">1 capsule\r\ndaily throughout pregnancy and lactation\r\nor as directed by the physician.</span></p><br><p><strong>Packing : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Ferospan 6 x 10''s capsules in\r\nblister pack.</span></p>', 'uploads/images/ferospan.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 02:53:34', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 4, 'uploads/IMG/ferospan.jpg'),
(1089, 'Ferozi', 322, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Ferozi timed release\r\ncapsule is a combination of blended\r\npellets of dried Ferrous Sulphate 150mg,\r\nFolic Acid 500mcg & Zinc Sulphate\r\nMonohydrate 61.8mg (Eq to 22.5mg\r\nzinc).</span></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Indication : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">Ferozi is indicated for the\r\ntreatment and prophylaxis of iron, folic\r\nacid and zinc deficiency, specially during\r\npregnancy and lactation.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, " helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;"=""><strong>Dosage and administration : </strong><span class="redactor-invisible-space">1 capsule\r\ndaily throughout pregnancy and lactation\r\nor as directed by the physician.</span></p><p><strong>Packing </strong><strong>:</strong>  <em>Ferozi : </em>6 x 10''s capsules in blister pack.</p>', 'uploads/images/ferozi.jpg', 1, '2017-11-29 02:52:03', NULL, NULL, '', 'Y', 4, 'uploads/IMG/ferozi.jpg'),
(1090, 'Neoplat', 37, '<p><strong></strong><strong>Composition : </strong>Each Metered dose (Puff) contains Beclometasone Dipropionate 100 mcg.</p><p><strong></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong>Indication : </strong>Becovent is indicated in the maintenance treatment of asthma as prophylactic therapy in patients 5 years of age and older. Becovent is also indicated for asthma patients who require systemic corticosteroid administration, where adding Becovent may reduce or eliminate the need for the systemic corticosteroids.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong>Dosage and administration :</strong> Becovent inhaler is for oral inhalation use only. Patients should be given a starting dose of inhaled Becovent appropriate to the severity of their disease. The dose may then be adjusted until control is achieved or reduced to the minimum effective dose according to individual response. Management of chronic asthma (Adults & Children over 12 years): 100-400 mcg twice daily. Maximum 1000 mcg twice daily. Children (5-12 years): 100-200 mcg twice daily. the dose may be adjusted as necessary.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong>Use in pregnancy and lactation :</strong> Administration of drugs during pregnancy and lactation should only be considered if the expected benefit to the mother is greater than any possible risk to the foetus or child. There is insufficient experience of the use of Salmeterol Xinafoate and Fluticasone Propionate in human pregnancy and lactation. There are no data available for human breast milk.<strong></strong></p><p><strong>Packing : </strong>Becovent HFA Inhaler : Each box contains one inhaler of 200 Puffs</p>', 'uploads/images/neoplat.jpg', 1, '2017-11-09 23:10:26', NULL, NULL, 'Y', 'Y', 4, 'uploads/IMG/neoplat.jpg'),
